Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.46,0:48:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好软
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.34,0:48:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.12,0:49:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-好舒服 -舒服吗？\N-是的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.04,0:49:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-奶子舒服吗？-舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.76,0:50:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.28,0:50:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,从后面插进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.83,0:50:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.95,0:51:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.70,0:51:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.42,0:51:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了 要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.30,0:52:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.02,0:52:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.22,0:52:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-后入我 -后入吗？
