Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.53,0:52:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.17,0:53:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-好舒服 -好舒服\N-好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.96,0:53:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
