Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.43,0:59:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我挂了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.79,1:00:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-好漂亮 -谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.75,1:00:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好厉害
