Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.89,1:47:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,插进去了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.73,1:48:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,夹住手指了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:16.33,1:48:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.77,1:48:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,很想射吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.13,1:48:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这么舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.56,1:49:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这么硬
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.32,1:49:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.36,1:49:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:49:49.20,1:49:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这么可爱的表情是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.52,1:49:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-这么舒服吗？ -是的
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.91,1:50:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢舒服的事情吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.55,1:50:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这么想射吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.95,1:50:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-要射了 -什么要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.55,1:50:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉有奇怪的东西要出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.59,1:50:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都行 出来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.43,1:51:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,射了好多
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.90,1:51:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,还能射更多吧
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.82,1:51:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞 这么湿
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.62,1:51:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-不行了 -没有了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.30,1:51:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-已经不行了 -已经不行了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.90,1:51:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,射了这么多
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.58,1:52:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.62,1:52:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,(S1 葵)
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.54,1:52:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢您今天的指名
Dialogue: 0,1:52:17.50,1:52:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我是葵
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.65,1:52:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,会好好服务的 请享受吧
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.13,1:52:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 我开始了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.03,1:55:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我开始了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:58.61,1:57:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,1:58:41.92,1:58:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这么硬
Dialogue: 0,1:58:51.28,1:58:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,可以帮我脱下吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:59:18.27,1:59:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可以用奶子夹住吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:59:57.15,1:59:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:00:00.03,2:00:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,2:00:18.03,2:00:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,2:00:46.46,2:00:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,2:00:51.86,2:00:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢这样慢慢的吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:00:54.74,2:00:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,2:00:58.34,2:01:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:03:22.32,2:03:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不得了
Dialogue: 0,2:03:45.35,2:03:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,2:03:51.11,2:03:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,2:04:04.07,2:04:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-不得了 -要射了吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:04:11.27,2:04:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,2:04:14.15,2:04:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,先忍住
Dialogue: 0,2:04:47.27,2:04:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:05:27.58,2:05:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,射出来了呢
Dialogue: 0,2:06:03.21,2:06:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 为你清洗干净吧
Dialogue: 0,2:06:10.41,2:06:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,可以帮我脱下吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:06:32.37,2:06:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-这样可以吗？ -是的
Dialogue: 0,2:06:44.97,2:06:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-那么 这边请 -好的
Dialogue: 0,2:06:54.33,2:06:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-请坐 -好
Dialogue: 0,2:07:06.57,2:07:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-水温合适吗？ -是的
Dialogue: 0,2:07:54.08,2:07:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,2:08:18.20,2:08:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这边请
Dialogue: 0,2:08:20.35,2:08:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,2:08:30.79,2:08:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我开始了
Dialogue: 0,2:08:37.27,2:08:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-不冷吗？ -热热的 很舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:09:28.03,2:09:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我开始了
Dialogue: 0,2:10:51.53,2:10:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,2:11:03.05,2:11:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-舒服吗？ -是的
Dialogue: 0,2:11:08.09,2:11:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,2:12:26.56,2:12:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-好躁动 -躁动吗？\N-是的
Dialogue: 0,2:13:27.39,2:13:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,知道腿被奶子顶着吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:13:30.99,2:13:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:17:23.52,2:17:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,如何 屁眼舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:20:17.37,2:20:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,转过来
Dialogue: 0,2:20:20.25,2:20:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,2:20:25.65,2:20:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,2:22:00.32,2:22:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,2:24:25.37,2:24:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,越来越硬了
Dialogue: 0,2:25:28.73,2:25:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-我用屁股了 -好
Dialogue: 0,2:26:35.32,2:26:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,2:27:04.11,2:27:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:27:35.79,2:27:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,插进来了
Dialogue: 0,2:27:51.26,2:27:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,2:28:07.82,2:28:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:28:36.62,2:28:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,2:28:47.42,2:28:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:29:07.57,2:29:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:30:08.76,2:30:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:30:19.56,2:30:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,插好深
Dialogue: 0,2:30:39.72,2:30:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,湿湿的
Dialogue: 0,2:30:51.60,2:30:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,湿湿的 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:31:12.48,2:31:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:32:05.03,2:32:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-插得深吗？ -是的
Dialogue: 0,2:32:19.43,2:32:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,2:32:29.14,2:32:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,湿湿的
Dialogue: 0,2:33:11.98,2:33:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:33:59.49,2:34:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:34:17.13,2:34:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:34:38.01,2:34:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,2:36:33.19,2:36:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:36:44.71,2:36:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:36:47.95,2:36:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,2:36:50.83,2:36:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-要射了吗？ -是的
Dialogue: 0,2:37:20.34,2:37:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:37:36.54,2:37:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,2:38:19.01,2:38:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,射了好多
Dialogue: 0,2:38:22.61,2:38:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服 干净
Dialogue: 0,2:38:32.33,2:38:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这样做爱也不错吧
Dialogue: 0,2:38:46.01,2:38:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢您看到最后
Dialogue: 0,2:38:51.41,2:38:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,期待您的下次指名
